notifications.payin: Please make sure the currency you send is new ANT. The contract address for new ANT transfers is 0xa117000000f279d81a1d3cc75430faa017fa5a2e. Old ANT is not supported on Changelly anymore.

Please make sure the currency you send is a new AXS token. The contract address we support for AXS transfers is 0xbb0e17ef65f82ab018d8edd776e8dd940327b28b. Old AXS token is not supported on Changelly anymore.
Please note Changelly accepts only BCHN chain. BCHA payments won't be processed.
BTG exchanges can take about 7-8 hours due to the high number of confirmations required for the incoming BTG transactions.
BSV exchanges can take up to 6 hours due to the high number of confirmations required for the incoming BSV transactions.

Please note that CELO contract payments are not accepted by Changelly. Be sure to send CELO as an ordinary transfer only! CELO exchanges can take up to 2 hours due to the high number of confirmations required for the incoming CELO transactions.
NRG exchanges can take up to 84 hours due to the high number of confirmations required for the incoming NRG transactions.
Please note we accept FTM payments via Ethereum (ERC-20) network only. FTM sent via other networks CANNOT be processed or recovered.

Please note that this option must be used ONLY to exchange FLOKI on the BSC (bep-20) network. When a transaction is created using this option, FLOKI sent via other networks CANNOT be processed or recovered!
GALA sent via the old contract address will not be processed. The new GALA contract address is 0xd1d2Eb1B1e90B638588728b4130137D262C87cae. Please check before sending.
Please note that HT payments can be accepted via the ERC20 blockchain only. Huobi chain is NOT supported on Changelly.

Please note that IOTA deposit addresses should not be re-used. Always verify that youre depositing to a newly generated IOTA deposit address. We cannot credit IOTA tokens deposited to a previously used deposit address.
KMD exchanges can take about 2 hours due to the high number of confirmations required for the incoming KMD transactions.

notifications.payout: Please note that the XMR balance in your wallet may take a bit longer to update after the exchange is completed due to the nature of XMR network.

NEO is an indivisible currency. It means that it should represent a whole number. The final figure is always rounded down to the next lower integer, if NEO price rises. To minimize the risk of a sudden price drop affecting final amounts, we recommend you to put a little extra for the more reliable result.

notifications.payin: Please make sure that the currency you send is MainNet ONT coin. Please do not send old ONT (NEO token), for we don't support it anymore. Sent ONG CANNOT be processed or recovered.
NB: on Changelly, ARRR does not require a memo! Please make sure to leave the memo field blank, since any irrelevant data placed in this field will make your deposit invisible to us.

Please note that this option must be used ONLY to exchange MATIC on the Ethereum (ERC-20) network. When a transaction is created using this option, MATIC sent via other networks CANNOT be processed or recovered! To exchange the Polygon version, please select MATICPOLYGON.

Please note that this option must be used ONLY to exchange MATIC on the Polygon network. When a transaction is created using this option, MATIC sent via other networks CANNOT be processed or recovered! To exchange the Ethereum version, please select MATIC.
Please note that TFUEL contract payments are not accepted by Changelly. Be sure to send TFUEL as an ordinary transfer only!
Please note that TRX contract payments are not accepted by Changelly. Be sure to send TRX as an ordinary transfer only!

Do note that TUSDTRX and USDTRX are different currencies! Please be sure to understand which coin you wish to exchange before creating a transaction! USDTRX sent to a TUSDTRX address and vice versa cannot be accepted.
Please note that we accept only Native USDC Arbitrum token, not the Bridged USDC Arbitrum. Sending Bridged USDCARB on our USDCARB address may result in the loss of your funds!
Please note that we support XVS based on the contract address 0xcf6bb5389c92bdda8a3747ddb454cb7a64626c63 only. Any alternative contracts CANNOT be accepted.

notifications.payout: Please do not forget to paste the XRP destination tag provided by your wallet. If the tag is required by your wallet yet is missing in your recipient data, your Ripples will not be delivered.
